Director:Philip G. Atwell

Writers (WGA):Lee Anthony Smith (written by) &amp;
Gregory J. Bradley (written by)

Release Date:24 August 2007 (USA) 

Genre:Action / Thriller

Plot Outline :After his partner Tom Wynne (Terry Chen) and family are killed apparently by the infamous and elusive assassin Rogue (Jet Li), FBI agent Jack Crawford (Jason Statham) becomes obsessed with revenge as his world unravels into a vortex of guilt and betrayal. Rogue eventually resurfaces to settle a score of his own, setting off a bloody crime war between Asian mob rivals Chang (John Lone) of the Triad&amp;#039;s and Yakuza boss Shiro (Ryo Ishibashi). When Jack and Rogue finally come face to face, the ultimate truth of their pasts will be revealed.

Runtime: 103 min 

Country: USA 

Language: English

Subtitles: Bulgarian and Turkish

